items.title: Maruti Suzuki adds six airbags to Ertiga and Baleno, increases prices
items.description: The country’s largest carmaker said the move will lead to an average ex-showroom price increase of 1.4 percent for Ertiga and 0.5 percent for Baleno.

items.title: Amendments to nuclear laws still in the works, unlikely this monsoon session
items.description: The overhaul of India's nuclear laws to bring in private participation also raises questions over accountability for the imported reactors that would be supplied by a foreign technology or design partner.

items.title: ICICI Lombard Q1 FY26: Growth slows across segments; retail health stands out
items.description: Given that ICICI Lombard’s market share in the retail health business is a mere 3.5 percent compared to over 30 percent for Star Health and over 9 percent for HDFC ERGO, there is a long runway for growth.

items.title: Rs 200 ticket fallout: Karnataka’s move could dent PVR Inox revenues, exhibitors urge for dialogue
